                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5c59d72c-f4e4-11e3-bddd-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5c59d72c-f4e4-11e3-bddd-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_7d failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;test_7d.3: Cannot do &apos;lost&apos; operations&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;est_7d.3 first: mkdir /mnt/lustre/d7d.replay-vbr/f7d.replay-vbr-0; rmdir /mnt/lustre/d7d.replay-vbr/f7d.replay-vbr-0
