test_7d.3 lost: createmany -o /mnt/lustre2/d7d.replay-vbr/f7d.replay-vbr- 1; mv /mnt/lustre2/d7d.replay-vbr/f7d.replay-vbr-0 /mnt/lustre2/d7d.replay-vbr/f7d.replay-vbr-1
CMD: shadow-47vm1 createmany -o /mnt/lustre2/d7d.replay-vbr/f7d.replay-vbr- 1; mv /mnt/lustre2/d7d.replay-vbr/f7d.replay-vbr-0 /mnt/lustre2/d7d.replay-vbr/f7d.replay-vbr-1
shadow-47vm1: mv: cannot stat `/mnt/lustre2/d7d.replay-vbr/f7d.replay-vbr-0&apos;: No such file or directory
open(/mnt/lustre2/d7d.replay-vbr/f7d.replay-vbr-0) error: No such file or directory
total: 0 creates in 0.00 seconds: 0.00 creates/second
 replay-vbr test_7d: @@@@@@ FAIL: test_7d.3: Cannot do &apos;lost&apos; operations 
&lt;/pre&gt;
